{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 30,
  "title": "第三十章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "以道佐人主者，不以兵強天下。"
    },
    {
      "text": "其事好還。"
    },
    {
      "text": "師之所處，荊棘生焉。大軍之後，必有凶年。"
    },
    {
      "text": "善有果而已，不敢以取強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而勿矜，果而勿伐，果而勿驕。"
    },
    {
      "text": "果而不得已，果而勿強。"
    },
    {
      "text": "物壯則老，是謂不道，不道早已。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 14
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以道佐人主，尚不可以兵强於天下，況人主躬於道者乎。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "為始者務欲立功生事，而有道者務欲還反無為，故云，其事好還也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 20
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言師凶害之物也。無有所濟，必有所傷，賊害人民，殘荒田畝，故曰荊棘生焉。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 12
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "果猶濟也。言善用師者，趣以濟難而已矣，不以兵力取强於天下也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "吾不以師道為尚，不得已而用，何矜驕之有也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-6",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 5,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言用兵雖趣功果濟難，然時故不得已，當復用者，但當以除暴亂，不遂用果以為强也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-7",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 6,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 15
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "壯，武力暴興，喻以兵强於天下者也。飄風不終朝，驟雨不終日，故暴興必不道早已也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
